data.description: Charming cottage in a prime location nestled on 2 acres on a cul de sac. Perfectly situated between Armonk, Bedford, and Greenwich, offering the ultimate convenience. Whether you prefer to move in and relish the cozy charm as is or create your dream home, this home offers endless possibilities. Inside, the spacious interior provides the ease of one-floor living. Outside, enjoy the natural beauty that surrounds you on the front porch or in the level backyard. Don't miss the oversized detached 2-car garage featuring a large studio space ideal for a home office. 50 minutes to NYC. 38 minutes express trains from North White Plains train station.
